ass=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bfantasystoriesforum.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=rillen>Rillen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Weaver of Flames</span><br>  Posts: 179<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/6/02 7:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> eq modified rp</span><hr size=1> OOC (Well, I recently read the new trilogy by margaret wiess and tracy hickman and I really loved the idea.  The gods have left the world.  Conventional magic and clerical powers are GONE, but wild magic and healing of the heart have replaced the gifts of the gods.  New factions are emerging and the world is but a pot, ready to boil over.  In my adaptation for Eq, The city of freeport has joined with Neriak, Ogguk, and the troll town whose name I can't remember.  The elves of Felwithe and Kelethin are at war, the dwarves have allied with thsoe of Kelethin and the gnomes with those of Felwithe.  The erudites of Odus have forsaken the ideals of good and evil and have created a new city.  The forest of toxullia is gone.  The two cities have joined together to create a metropolis of power and intellegence.  Were once had been wood, is now a giant city of beauty.  The halflings are, well, the same.  Halas was destroyed and what remains of the barbarians is tribes scattered throughout the everfrost.  The coldain have been destroyed and the dragons and giants on Velious are no longer at war, although they are the least of allies.  The iksar believe it was their failure as subjects to Cazic that caused his dissapearance.  They are planning to mount an attack on Antonica to strike fear so that they may once again regain their gods favor.  The geography is otherwise the same as are all the leaders.  Oh, there are also 2 tunnels leading from kaladim to kelethin and another from ak'anon to felwithe.  Well, I hope you like the idea and post!)  <br>
<br>
Oh and magic no longer requires words and hand motions.  It comes from within, but I will leave that open for you to tweak yourselves!<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ) <p>Ignis Summa Pugnabat, The fires shall cleanse the world.</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bfantasystoriesforum.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=rillen>Rillen</A> at: 8/6/02 8:00:58 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ubellonakali.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bellona Kali</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Child of Hate</span><br>  Posts: 409<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/6/02 9:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://auction.2y.net/user/paradisetheheretic/Reineva.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: eq modified rp</span><hr size=1> ~*(wild magic? healing of the heart? sounds kinda fruity to me... hehe, it's an *awsome* idea! ^.^ I just don't wanna be the one to start it out :P hehe. Will post once someone else does <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )*~ <p><Br> <Br> <Br> <Br> <i>Never will fish heads be seen sitting in itallian resturants conversing with oriental women</i><br><br>
