<br>
For only a moment, he couldn't do anything but stare.  Her cloths were somewhat torn and ratty, and she appeared somewhat thin.  Nothing major, but enough to get Undeen's mind going.  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Perhaps she lives on her own...  How long then, since last she ate?  Or bathed?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
