There was a battle surrounding Brutus. Two spears were strapped to his back, channeling all the natural energies into his mind. He could feel the spirits speak at his back, and they followed *HIM* now, NOT some &quot;god&quot; or &quot;council&quot;. They had abandoned them; Brutus would not. He held a third spear on his shoulders, ready for use.<br>
